data.description: Remarkable Cape Cod home situated just a few minutes from Fort Drum. Private setting with 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms sitting on 1.56 acres of land. Fresh paint through ought the interior. This home includes a spacious heated 2 car attached garage, 2 fireplaces, central air, first floor laundry, metal roof installed less than 5 years ago, and water heater less than 2 years old. Plus a Florida sun room that leads to the in-ground pool. This one won't last long. Call today!
